        <p>
          We were very thankful for the car we were driving, a new Chrysler with a camera for
          reversing. We put it to very good use that night. It's how we managed to not run over
          huge rocks or get stuck in deep holes in the rocky dirt roads. I think we probably
          drove around the area for an hour before we finally found our house.
        </p>
        <p>
          When we walked in, we all relaxed immediately. We were happy that we wouldn't be
          sleeping in the car that night and the house was so cozy.
        </p>
